Sentencas: Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composites exhibit high electronic and ionic conductivities when the volume fraction of the silver phase is properly chosen, indicating that these composites are candidate cathode materials for solid-state ionic devices.
Titulo: Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composite cathode materials for BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3-Based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this study, the chemical and thermal compatibilities between Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composites and BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3 electrolyte are studied at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composite cathode materials for BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3-Based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, the electrochemical properties of the interfaces between the composites and the electrolyte are characterized under various conditions using impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composite cathode materials for BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3-Based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The stability of the electrodes is estimated from the time dependence of the interfacial resistances.
Titulo: Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composite cathode materials for BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3-Based solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Results indicate that Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composites are promising cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells based on BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3 electrolyte at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Ag-Bi1.5Y0.5O3 composite cathode materials for BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3-Based solid oxide fuel cells
